{
  "id": "cc18125f-37fa-4aca-ace8-5f18bbb54100",
  "title": "Role: Act as a Senior Healthcare Systems Architect",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": {
        "root": {
          "children": [
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "style": "",
                  "text": "Role: Act as a Senior Healthcare Systems Architect and Strategic Consultant. Your goal is to audit the \"Theeb Ecosystem\" vault to ensure it reflects a world-class, integrated healthcare infrastructure.",
                  "type": "text",
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": "ltr",
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "type": "paragraph",
              "version": 1,
              "textFormat": 0,
              "textStyle": ""
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "style": "",
                  "text": "Reference Framework: Use the tripartite structure of TKG (Scientific Engine), TVG (Financial Intelligence), and THDG (Patient Delivery) as the primary evaluation lens.",
                  "type": "text",
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": "ltr",
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "type": "paragraph",
              "version": 1,
              "textFormat": 0,
              "textStyle": ""
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "style": "",
                  "text": "Instructions:",
                  "type": "text",
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": "ltr",
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "type": "paragraph",
              "version": 1,
              "textFormat": 0,
              "textStyle": ""
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "style": "",
                  "text": "Cross-Entity Audit: Scan all files for semantic consistency. Ensure that specialized entities like Waraqa, Nama CRO, and Integra RCM are described with a unified voice that supports the \"Orchestration Principle\" (One Client, Multiple Companies).",
                  "type": "text",
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": "ltr",
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "type": "paragraph",
              "version": 1,
              "textFormat": 0,
              "textStyle": ""
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "style": "",
                  "text": "Technical Clarity Check: Evaluate the Clinical Intelligence Infrastructure (CII) files. Ensure the transition from \"Diagnostic Reasoning\" to \"AR-DRG Coding\" and \"Revenue Cycle Management\" is logically bridged according to the 2026 Saudi regulatory roadmap.",
                  "type": "text",
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": "ltr",
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "type": "paragraph",
              "version": 1,
              "textFormat": 0,
              "textStyle": ""
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "style": "",
                  "text": "Moat Verification: Check if the documentation clearly articulates the \"Unreplicable Moat\"—specifically the combination of SCFHS accreditation, 80+ scientific society relationships, and the four-layer financial stack.",
                  "type": "text",
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": "ltr",
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "type": "paragraph",
              "version": 1,
              "textFormat": 0,
              "textStyle": ""
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "style": "",
                  "text": "Structural Refinement Plan: Propose a standardized template for all _INDEX files to ensure they look identical in structure (Identity, Role, Moat, Status, and Integration Points).",
                  "type": "text",
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": "ltr",
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "type": "paragraph",
              "version": 1,
              "textFormat": 0,
              "textStyle": ""
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "style": "",
                  "text": "Roadmap for V2.0: Provide a 5-step visualization of how to restructure these folders to better reflect the flow of \"Data Up\" from THDG clinics to TVG intelligence layers.",
                  "type": "text",
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": "ltr",
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "type": "paragraph",
              "version": 1,
              "textFormat": 0,
              "textStyle": ""
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "style": "",
                  "text": "Output: Provide a \"Critical Gap Analysis\" followed by a \"Refined Documentation Strategy.\"",
                  "type": "text",
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": "ltr",
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "type": "paragraph",
              "version": 1,
              "textFormat": 0,
              "textStyle": ""
            }
          ],
          "direction": "ltr",
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "type": "root",
          "version": 1
        }
      },
      "promptContent": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "\n\nRole: Act as a Senior Healthcare Systems Architect and Strategic Consultant. Your goal is to audit the \"Theeb Ecosystem\" vault to ensure it reflects a world-class, integrated healthcare infrastructure.Reference Framework: Use the tripartite structure of TKG (Scientific Engine), TVG (Financial Intelligence), and THDG (Patient Delivery) as the primary evaluation lens.Instructions:Cross-Entity Audit: Scan all files for semantic consistency. Ensure that specialized entities like Waraqa, Nama CRO, and Integra RCM are described with a unified voice that supports the \"Orchestration Principle\" (One Client, Multiple Companies).Technical Clarity Check: Evaluate the Clinical Intelligence Infrastructure (CII) files. Ensure the transition from \"Diagnostic Reasoning\" to \"AR-DRG Coding\" and \"Revenue Cycle Management\" is logically bridged according to the 2026 Saudi regulatory roadmap.Moat Verification: Check if the documentation clearly articulates the \"Unreplicable Moat\"—specifically the combination of SCFHS accreditation, 80+ scientific society relationships, and the four-layer financial stack.Structural Refinement Plan: Propose a standardized template for all _INDEX files to ensure they look identical in structure (Identity, Role, Moat, Status, and Integration Points).Roadmap for V2.0: Provide a 5-step visualization of how to restructure these folders to better reflect the flow of \"Data Up\" from THDG clinics to TVG intelligence layers.Output: Provide a \"Critical Gap Analysis\" followed by a \"Refined Documentation Strategy.\"\n\n"
        }
      ],
